dotnetType.name: IBinarySerializerBuilderCase
dotnetType.summary:
Builds Avro serializers for specific type-schema combinations. Used by
            <see cref="T:Chr.Avro.Serialization.BinarySerializerBuilder" /> to break apart serializer building logic.

returns.summary:
An action that accepts an object and a <see cref="T:System.IO.Stream" /> and writes the serialized
            object to the stream.

overloads.summary: Builds a serializer for a type-schema pair.
Determines whether the case can be applied to a schema.
Determines whether the case can be applied to a type resolution.
